               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18370814-name-698" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18370814-name-698" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18370814-name-698" type="surname" value="JOHNSON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18370814-name-698" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY JOHNSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. On the 17th of July I sent for the prisoner to help my wife remove a few things from the house—I left my handkerchief hanging on the chair, and missed it—I went the next morning to the prisoner's mother, and he was gone out—I went to the pawnbroker's, and found it—this is it.</p>
               <p>
