                  </hi>. I have heard what my husband has stated—it is correct I have known the prisoner upwards of two 3 years—I lived with his mother as a lodger—the value of this handkerchief is 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.</p>
