               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi> (<hi rend="italic">written</hi>,) "The prisoner begs to state that, being hired to remove the prosecutor's goods, for which he was to receive 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; and the prosecutor not being willing to pay him, he was induced to take the handkerchief and pawn it, intending to get it out when the prosecutor paid him."</p>
